 to eat verant's shit for over a year and a half, then to be able to cut off the money I send them every month.  <br>  <br> Qalar Rubican  <br> Cats in Hats  <br> Drinal Server <br> -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- <br>  <br>  <br>  <br>  <br> PS. I've read a few other statements by other people who claim that certain scripts were &quot;supposed&quot; to be initiated at certain events. IE Dain's Death, Tormax's Death, Sleeper's Awakening. Scripts = Upon Tormax's Death NPC dwarves storm Kael in a mock battle and things like that along the lines of the Coldain Ring quest final battle.  <br> <p></p><span class="SignatureTitle">-----signature-----</span><div class="SignatureText">Throes, 60 enchanter, Xev, 60 druid, Xev <br> Flintnilf, 60 wizard,  Harmonium <br> Cruelty, world#1, MSN gaming zone, Age Of Empires (retired) <br>  <br> </div></td></tr><tr align="right" valign="bottom"><td colspan=2 class="BoardRowB"><a class="BoardRowBLink" href="/help/default.asp?goto=faqs%2Easp%23lockedtopic">Locked Topic</a> | <a href="/active_topic_notify.asp?mes=9446454" class="BoardRowBLink">Active Topic Notification</a> | <a class="BoardRowBLink" href="/pm_send.asp?usr=6691">Private Message</a> | <a class="BoardRowBLink" href="/user_posts.asp?usr=6691">Post History</a></td></tr><tr align="left" valign="top" class="BoardRowA"><td class="BoardRowA" rowspan=3 width="17%"><a href=" http://users.ign.com/about/Throes?boards=vn " class="AuthorLink">Throes</a>&nbsp;<a href="/help/default.asp?goto=faqs%2Easp%23stars"><img align=absmiddle src=http://media.ign.com/boardimages/star3.gif border=0 hspace=0 vspace=0 alt="933 posts"></a><br><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><!-- WISH & COLL STUFF --><table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tr class="BoardRowA"><td nowrap="false" class="BoardRowA"><a class="BoardRowBLink" href="http://users.ign.com/collection/Throes"><font size="1">collection (0)</font></a> | <a class="BoardRowBLink